Second Department,

October, 1957

(October 1, 1957) In the Matter of John Tortorelli et al., Petitioners, against Fred J. Munder, as County Judge of County of Suffolk, Respondent.

Proceeding pursuant to article 78 of the Civil Practice Act to review the postponement by a County Judge of the trial of a summary proceeding to recover possession of real property and to order him to direct that the summary proceeding be set for trial for a day certain. Proceeding dismissed, without costs (Civ. Prae. Act, § 1285; Code Grim. Pro., § 7-a; Judiciary Law, § 190). Present — Nolan, P. J., Wenzel, Beldock, Murphy and Ughetta, JJ.
